            . I am an officer. I was by <placeName id="t18210718-141-crimeloc792">Sadler's Wells</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18210718-141-crimeloc792" type="placeName" value="Sadler's Wells"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18210718-141-crimeloc792" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210718-141-off790 t18210718-141-crimeloc792"></join>, and saw the prisoners, and three more together. They went one on each side of a servant, who was carrying a child, one put his hand to the child's neck; they saw me, drew back, then went up again. Morris made a snatch at the child's neck, and took the necklace off; they crossed the road; I followed and saw it drop between them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210718-141-person1233">
